Name: Ctrl CV
About the game: 'What would you feel if, all of a sudden, there were a stockpile of people looking just like you on the streets?' Welcome to the world of Ctrl CV , a find-the-image platformer puzzle game. You are surrounded by countless clones of yourself, and your goal is to find the source of these doppelgangers. Try not to lose yourself in the midst of 'yourselves' . We do not know if you're one of them, or if it really is the true you... But one thing is certain; that there's only one of you that truly exist.
